title: Photos: Rangers look calm in stretches before key ALDS Game 5
text: Texas Rangers right fielder Shin-Soo Choo, left, gets some help in loosening up from strength and conditioning coach Jose Vazquez before Game 5 of the ALDS between the Texas Rangers and the Toronto Blue Jays at Rogers Centre in Toronto, Canada on Wednesday, October 14, 2015. (Louis DeLuca/The Dallas Morning News)
